  textVersion  =
  paste("Pierre-Yves Hernvann, Didier Gascuel, Dorothee Kopp, Marianne Robert, Etienne Rivot (2022).",    "EcoDiet: A hierarchical Bayesian model to combine stomach, biotracer, and literature data into diet matrix estimation."))
        
